Use Grant:
  Human use is permitted — personal, educational, professional, even
  commercial — as long as a human is in the loop, interacting with
  the forest one piece at a time.
  Forking and modification for human use is permitted.

Anti-Automation Clause:
  Mass automated generation is NOT permitted, regardless of
  commercial status. This includes:
    · scraping the source code to extract prompt logic for bulk runs
    · headless browser / Selenium / Playwright bulk pipelines
    · server-side fetch loops that treat this work as an API endpoint
    · any non-interactive batch generation that strips the human
      DNA layer from the loop

  Bots may read the source code (it is open). They may not turn this
  pool into a data extraction target.

After the Change Date, the Licensed Work will automatically be made
available under the Change License.

Full BSL 1.1 text:  https://mariadb.com/bsl11/

---

Forest Spirit Note (non-binding, philosophical):

  This forest is a pool, not an API.
  Humans are welcome to enter, dwell, grow with it, take a seedling.
  Bots are welcome to read; please do not strip-mine the data
  to mass-generate derivative versions devoid of human DNA.

  The skeleton is open. The light you bring is yours alone.
  Your light × the forest's skeleton = only your forest.
